Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.87,0:00:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.14,0:00:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.34,0:00:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.02,0:00:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞過危險的轉角 追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.49,0:00:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.39,0:00:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.13,0:00:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.08,0:00:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.61,0:00:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.18,0:00:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.75,0:01:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.69,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.32,0:01:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.23,0:01:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.93,0:01:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.64,0:01:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟這個男人一起拍照有這麼快樂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.43,0:01:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的表情都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他正如其名是難民的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.37,0:01:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本我們這邊不是叫他久世英雄而是叫他「朗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.64,0:01:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時像「狼」一般無情凶殘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.82,0:02:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時像晴天般晴「朗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.22,0:02:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是又像不知何時會到處遊蕩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去蹤影的流「浪」漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此難民們這麼稱呼他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.45,0:02:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,＃17 修好母子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,台灣當局也是到最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才注意到這個男子的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難民跟地方角頭達成共識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始在馬路上走動的時候出現奇怪的傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.17,0:02:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「有一個能領導難民像是指導者一般的男子」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始只是這樣的傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不久之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難民們開始頻頻犯下走私案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.71,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且出現跟地方角頭之間有組織的抗爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼著我們有必要去調查那個傳言的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是確認了久世的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.06,0:03:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始還以為這樣很好\N至少難民不會惹是生非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻大傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們到最近為止還不過是船民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻不論在與陸地的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是跟角頭之間的抗爭方式上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都一口氣升級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這一切的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在這個男人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我不得不承認他是一個了不起的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C4塑膠炸彈的走私管道也是他建立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用改裝漁船來做海盜行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.22,0:03:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經是難民的拿手好戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 對我們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「朗」願意自行離開台灣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫了我們一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 對日本公安就得表示哀悼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久世離開這裡的理由為何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據那些人所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.88,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為了保養義體不得不回日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 是真是假沒人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切合情合理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 很有參考價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於你回程的機票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不巧今天沒有航班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改明天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如你知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.04,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟大陸的邦交好不容易開始正常化卻出現日美安保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火星飛得到的範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常發生有火藥味的事件乃是世上的常態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國際線的航班管理也因此無法照原定班表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.09,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以替繁忙的公安職員擠出休息的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一天就去觀光一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要一個人跑到難民街去閒逛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條街已經沒有更多情報了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.14,0:05:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想調查的話 要往西去大陸旅行看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在各地的難民街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說到現在還是四處都有歡迎那傢伙的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.15,0:05:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他實際上並沒有被全世界通緝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有人去確認這件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.30,0:05:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現在長崎的中樞電腦 我想多半就是久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是以這邊的難民來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多老人和小孩都沒有電子腦化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 他是如何讓他們跟自己的思考同步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我在這裡工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我們的交換條件嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對小孩子也毫不留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把偷來的東西物歸原主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不叫作交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說 東西在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東西在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.06,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你負責到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那群人叫作「小傑幫」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這附近的新興幫派角頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了那種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是會回來做更嚴厲的報復嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是我做的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我靜靜地看你的手被砍下來比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從某個角度來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.15,0:07:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次光一隻手可能解決不了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算恩將仇報嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姊姊難道是全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到這種高級貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定以後要像「朗」那樣換成全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不過是少一條手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「朗」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識「朗」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問問題的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想請你負責到底而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是絕種動物EX系列的青海龜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是EW系列的鴕鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得很不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就等上色之後出貨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.59,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是大戰前製作的真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.83,0:09:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟真品比較起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼做 塗色上總有點粗糙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小地方的細節也會被塗壞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 上面有刻印和型號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來幾乎就像真品不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這全都是可卡因做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用壓力成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是以前墨西哥一帶常用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這種模型 就算大人帶著也不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想出來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是「朗」想出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這是第一次實際進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼做是想讓我分享重大秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬拉我進來當同夥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.34,0:10:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姊姊不可能是「小傑」或「黃龍」的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.35,0:10:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是既不是難民也不是普通的旅客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要弄到全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你說不定知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非法弄到那種義體的渠道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.13,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你弄到全身義體想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想繼承「朗」想做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛 這種時候打來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.07,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 多謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會躲到某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.74,0:10:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也消失一陣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.61,0:10:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙都是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.28,0:10:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會注意到這是什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.89,0:11:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小傑幫那些人好像找到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像中更氣派呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 為什麼到這種地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去我藏身的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡比那種地方安全多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我頂樓的套房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,套房嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白金卡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姊姊你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.06,0:12:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的教育方針就是不讓小孩叫我媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽很年輕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛跟日本進行的會談當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.22,0:12:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日美安保締結後的美軍駐軍問題成為焦點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日方的回應…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在鴕鳥只飼養來食用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過到本世紀初為止 它們還像這樣奔馳在草原上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護小鳥不受天敵傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,族群中最強的母鳥會收養所有的小鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.74,0:13:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你接下來打算怎麼辦\N把別的小鳥放在自己的小鳥旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借此留下最強的基因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被期待太多我會很傷腦筋 所以把話說在前頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天早上就要離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去跟警察說明清楚 請他們保護你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.50,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會保護一個難民的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難民在這世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪裡都沒有容身之處不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不過是給你們資產階級吃的鴕鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久世…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「朗」這麼教你的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在這裡是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既是英雄也是神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他建議你義體化的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.86,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 要做跟「朗」一樣的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須義體化才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是年輕莽撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.57,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「朗」說他自己在很久以前就已經死過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.97,0:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以剩下的靈魂之火要替理解自己的人燃燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.98,0:14:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對一切絕望的我來說 這句話彷彿給了我希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是複製品也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.18,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人有全部模仿的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像連電子腦化都沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼跟他的思考同步化的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡單啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟「朗」說話就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟他談過一次 大家都會喜歡上「朗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇特的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.74,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最初見到你的時候 覺得你跟「朗」很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要一個人做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.65,0:14:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「朗」也都是一個人戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨你高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.79,0:14:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以問你一個問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.68,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以做愛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想試試看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ID卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車子來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.79,0:16:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請開到機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到那傢伙挺有骨氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對久世的形象也瞭解了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正吸引他們的因素是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是Stand Alone Complex的一種嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕得上飛機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對來得及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本還是個愛撒嬌的小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司機先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以載我去這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起一件急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的交易用普通方法行不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果我沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.59,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們之中要有人接下這個計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照「朗」教我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以白白犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.43,0:17:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩讓我搜查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.00,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我還殘留著這樣的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是查？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:18:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.83,0:19:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您願意聽我冒昧的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 很有禮貌嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟初次跟您見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上以後將會是共同促進生意成功的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可還沒決定見你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真是個有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢 老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是用這種方式見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有可能成為夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不認為嗎 小傑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 您在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我們從一開始就沒有想跟黃龍會起衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就先殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再把同夥的小鬼們也宰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再來找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時間我不記得有叫女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不記得你們有叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 打擾您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓難民的血玷污這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份人情我有一天會用別的方式還給您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始談交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是昨天的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想用這個交換這孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便也請你們不要對難民報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要求就這兩項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果接受 我就會乖乖消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不行我就不得不用武力來逼你們答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.45,0:20:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的性子可是很急的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.53,0:21:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟「朗」是同一種人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如您所看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都會被幹掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.33,0:21:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要追了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.80,0:21:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知己知彼 百戰不殆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個交易已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「朗」應該沒有勸你義體化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.06,0:22:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更沒有要你做幾乎喪命的危險抗爭對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.33,0:22:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有勇氣也有才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 死了就什麼都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.10,0:22:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要放下自傲創造未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.87,0:22:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.48,0:23:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.16,0:23:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.70,0:23:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.97,0:23:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
